<item>
            <title>[PPLNS-7740] Create a Callminer Ingestion job for the new BulkAPI</title>
                <link>https://theverygroup.atlassian.net/browse/PPLNS-7740</link>
                <project id="20015" key="PPLNS">Data Enablement</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Callminer BulkAPI export jobs will push files to &lt;/p&gt;
{env}-lakehouse-holding-zone and a lakehouse-copy-file task will unpack and copy the files to {env}
&lt;p&gt;-lakehouse-landing-zone. The files will then need to be ingested from the landing zone and the data made available to Customer Care.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This task is to create the ingestion jobs that will load the data from the landing zone into Iceberg (&lt;b&gt;EMR Workflow&lt;/b&gt;) and then from Iceberg to Teradata (&lt;b&gt;Glue Workflow&lt;/b&gt;). There will be 5 tables to load for each of the 5 datatypes needed by Customer Care;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Contacts&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Categories&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Category_Components&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Scores&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Score_Indicators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class="panel" style="background-color: #deebff;border-width: 1px;"&gt;&lt;div class="panelContent" style="background-color: #deebff;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The files needed for the ingestion will include at least those listed above. Some additional files may be added after discussions with Customer Care. This will need to be confirmed before work begins for this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since the files will arrive in the landing folder in csv format, they will need to be converted into parquet format using the csv-to-parquet converter so they can be ingested using the EMR Workflow engine.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
